  "description": "A neuroimaging dataset implementing the Visual Attribute-Specific Contextual Trajectory Paradigm 2.0, designed to investigate visual perception and contextual processing. This raw BIDS-formatted dataset provides neuroimaging data collected during a visual attribute task with contextual manipulations, supporting research into how the brain processes visual information within different contextual frameworks.",
